    "In a real-world scenario, this set of concepts is unknown.",
    "However, a retrieval augmented generation (RAG) approach would be feasible to provide the model with the most relevant HPO terms as context.",
    "Further, our experiments did, however, show that ontology stratification strategies could be employed as an alternative to using the entire ontology -e.g., domain-specific selection.",
